# 26. Most likely training problems you’ll hit

## Problem 1: CUDA out of memory
Fix:
- reduce `max_seq_length` to 384
- reduce LoRA target modules
- keep batch size at 1
- increase grad accumulation
- close all other GPU apps

## Problem 2: tokenizer/chat template issues
Fix:
- ensure `messages` field is valid
- set `tokenizer.pad_token = tokenizer.eos_token`

## Problem 3: DPO fails
Fix:
- reduce DPO dataset size
- run only on SIS
- fall back to alignment-lite SFT

## Problem 4: no visible improvement
Fix:
- improve data quality
- add more domain-specific examples
- include stronger workflow and compliance examples
- reduce noisy template answers

